# How to use this in your setup:
# 1. Upload this .asc file to your ADLS container (e.g., keys/partner-public-key.asc)
# 2. Reference it in the EncryptAndRename API call: "pgpKeyPath": "keys/partner-public-key.asc"
# 3. Share this public key with partners who need to decrypt your files

# To export your own public key:
# gpg --armor --export test@example.com > public-key.asc
